    "text": "Flag Code Modernization Act of 2021\n\nThis bill revises provisions regarding customs and practices with respect to the American flag.\n\nAmong other changes, the bill permits U.S. postal workers to wear the flag on their uniforms and modifies provisions regarding the position and manner of display of the flag."
